   <conbody>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">To enter a new date:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b> to enter the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">User stack</b>. </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Use the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Arrow keys</b> to navigate to <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">Enter new
date</codeph>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Use the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Numpad</b> (Number 0-9 keys) to enter a new date,
the format is <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">YYMMDD</b>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b> to enter and confirm the new date. </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Back key</b> or wait 30 seconds to exit the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">User stack</b>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">After leaving the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">User stack</b> press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Clock/number
1 key</b> to view and verify the new date.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </p>
